{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_QmfpZUlRXrtDREO2dn6dzSy7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_eN3Em9JkJoB9WfKCSLKuBN15","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/reports/context/TST-001.pack.md","content":"# TST-001 Context Pack\n\n## Ticket\nTST-001\n\n## Slug\nfs-rbac-03-live-enforcement\n\n## Idea Note\nImplement FS-RBAC-03: enforce live RBAC across critical APIs and flow controls, add auditable role operations/403 trail, and synchronize frontend role guards with no-refresh session updates.\n\n## Source Artifacts\n- PRD: `aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md`\n- Status: draft\n\n## AIDD:CONTEXT_PACK (Initial)\n- FS-RBAC-03 spec requires live RBAC enforcement on critical API endpoints\n- Need to add audit logging for role operations and 403 responses\n- Frontend role guards must sync with session updates without page refresh\n- Ticket: TST-001\n\n## AIDD:RESEARCH_HINTS (Initial)\n- Paths: (to be determined by analyst)\n- Keywords: RBAC, roles, permissions, 403, audit, session, guards\n- Notes: Identify current RBAC implementation, API middleware structure, frontend auth flow\n\n## AIDD:NON_NEGOTIABLES\n- All critical APIs must enforce RBAC with 403 on violations\n- Role operations must be auditable\n- Frontend must reflect role changes without refresh\n\n## AIDD:GOALS (Draft)\n- Enforce live RBAC across critical APIs\n- Add auditable role operations trail\n- Synchronize frontend role guards with live session updates\n\n## AIDD:RISKS (Draft)\n- Performance impact of live RBAC checks → caching strategy\n- Session desync between backend/frontend → websocket/polling mechanism\n- Audit log storage growth → retention policy\n\n## AIDD:ACCEPTANCE (Draft)\n- AC-1: Critical APIs return 403 for unauthorized role access\n- AC-2: All role operations are logged with timestamp, user, action\n- AC-3: Frontend role guards update within 5 seconds of session change\n\n## AIDD:OPEN_QUESTIONS\n- Q1: Which APIs are considered \"critical\" and in scope?\n- Q2: What is the current RBAC implementation (library/custom)?\n- Q3: Frontend framework and current auth mechanism?\n- Q4: Audit log storage requirements (DB/file/external)?\n"}}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":25868,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":25868,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5835f2fc-8007-4bc0-a58f-4f6cb083388a","uuid":"a2712b4e-5292-4b54-a7d8-bf54e3d34dd3"}
