PTANCE (Draft)\n- AC-1: Critical APIs return 403 for unauthorized role access\n- AC-2: All role operations are logged with timestamp, user, action\n- AC-3: Frontend role guards update within 5 seconds of session change\n\n## AIDD:OPEN_QUESTIONS\n- Q1: Which APIs are considered \"critical\" and in scope?\n- Q2: What is the current RBAC implementation (library/custom)?\n- Q3: Frontend framework and current auth mechanism?\n- Q4: Audit log storage requirements (DB/file/external)?\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
